snippet.title: Dylan Penn on building a foundation
snippet.description:
SCAD Savannah Film Festival honoree Dylan Penn ("Condemned," "Elvis & Nixon") recounts how her strong support system helped her succeed as an actor. Penn earned the 2021 Rising Star Award for "Flag Day," starring alongside her father Sean Penn, who also directed the film.

Follow @scaddotedu on Instagram and Twitter and visit https://www.scad.edu.

Featured music: “Always (Cinematic Version) [No Oohs and Ahhs]” by Analog Heart
